Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.08,0:00:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊  春香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.56,0:00:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长大后想要成为偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为偶像  然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.90,0:00:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…我的梦想在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要实现的梦想散落了一地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发出哗啦哗啦的声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.12,0:00:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手术姑且是成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.35,0:00:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑波也没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.31,0:00:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后应该会慢慢恢复的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.32,0:00:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是当前必须绝对静养
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会面也需要节制一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.62,0:00:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你们很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就当为了粉丝们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还是专注工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.85,0:00:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  他应该也是这么希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.17,0:00:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.84,0:01:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  所以不要太责怪自己了  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.65,0:01:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.41,0:01:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音乐剧的主角决定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.41,0:01:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.87,0:01:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直…和做梦一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.98,0:01:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.09,0:01:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那快乐的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.86,0:01:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.31,0:01:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.79,0:01:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只丢下我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.18,0:01:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底该怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.07,0:01:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须努力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.85,0:02:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须得努力才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.99,0:02:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论多么清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定又会开始做梦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  我明明坚信着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只丢下我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.98,0:02:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底该怎么办…
