Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.43,0:02:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\1c&0&\an7\fs20\fad(0,100)}菊地真  对不起\N双海真美  对不起…\N水濑伊织  今天…\N萩原雪步  对不起\N高槻弥生  呜  抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:02:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\1c&0&\an7\fs20\fad(100,0)}三浦梓  对不起\N我那霸响  今天的练习\N双海亚美  对不起…\N秋月律子  今天的演唱会练习…\N四条贵音  今日的练习…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.21,0:03:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经…不行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\1c&0&\an7\fs18}发信人  制作人先生\N标题  Re：关于圣诞节party…\N新年演唱会的练习虽然很辛苦\N但是大家一起加油吧！\N圣诞节的party是休息的好机会\N可以的话希望大家能聚一聚\N大家全员集合的机会也少了\N期待与大家的见面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.80,0:03:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作人先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  音乐剧的练习想请假？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是音乐剧  可以的话其他工作也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想集中精力应对演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.91,0:03:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.67,0:03:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话  我们的演唱会会变得很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都没有怎么练习过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也有各自练习过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.22,0:03:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然缺少全员练习
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演唱会也不是说办不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  说不定这场演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是最后一次全员的演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  大家一起练习…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.34,0:04:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香太任性了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香可是主角啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.43,0:04:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香不在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.89,0:04:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人的练习也要中止了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希本想绝对要演主角的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.21,0:04:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.08,0:04:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是春香的演技更厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以美希才放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香自己却不珍惜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也想努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.45,0:04:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很高兴能获得主角的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家会各奔东西的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  就到演唱会结束就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是我  大家也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也要一起练习…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  不要强人所难了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然想请假这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作人员那边我会去恳求征得同意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演唱会结束后我会加倍…不  三倍努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香想要怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香有点奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香当上了偶像难道不高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在电视和广播还有各种地方闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不快乐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香完全不像是觉得快乐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果快乐的话  就不会有这样的表情了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的表情真的那么奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.06,0:05:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.07,0:05:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是那么快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本应该是快乐的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么时候开始的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.89,0:06:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.11,0:06:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  想要做什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.01,0:06:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香她？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有点混乱…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时让她放下工作休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么做才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.23,0:06:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shiny  Smile
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演唱会舞台降临到手机之上！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  OK
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然发过几次邮件了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.47,0:07:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却没有回信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  这次CM拍得真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.07,0:07:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天海君  情况怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然听说是身体不适…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是长期疾病吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我们也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.19,0:07:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  不过也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你们这样分开工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难知道对方的情况了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没问题的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你们自己这么红
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用拘泥于765事务所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都十分努力地完成自己的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  今天也不出门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家的话能帮我跑跑腿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:09:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去外面稍微呼吸下新鲜空气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪买的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底想做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会想要成为偶像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,货箱就在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,765事务所的人在这种地方干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.59,0:09:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我的家就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.31,0:09:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…今天休息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:10:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当红的时候还能这么悠闲地放假
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是游刃有余啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息的话就是说很闲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.85,0:10:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来我们的演唱会看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演唱会？在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.28,0:10:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方真是抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说换了事务所不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.46,0:10:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在的事务所拿不到什么好场地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在961事务所的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连一起制作舞台的同伴都不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样更不用说什么信赖了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以算是稍微向你们学习了一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢  团结力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.72,0:10:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴间的羁绊是你们力量的源泉对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.18,0:10:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:10:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  冬马
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.78,0:11:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  我们马上就会追上你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羁绊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.67,0:11:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外科2号的谷村先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请赶快来护士中心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.34,0:11:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  突然来打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  给大家添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.39,0:11:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会快点出院赶上来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.62,0:11:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作人先生这么乱动的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:12:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是有什么事呢  当听众的话我还是可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.19,0:12:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是某个家庭的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时总在一起  很要好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人摔倒  马上有人伸手帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知从什么时候开始  这个家庭的成员各散东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个总是第一时间向别人伸出援手的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正独自苦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大家却遥远到无法来帮助她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的话说不定还能挽回
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这是正确的吗  自己能做得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:12:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:13:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都没有和家人好好相处过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没什么信心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早非常喜欢那个家人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.51,0:13:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  对我非常重要  非常的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一定都有和千早一样的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人就是这么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.86,0:13:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的  你相信着大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.26,0:13:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是家人  那就要把重要的话好好说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.02,0:13:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.02,0:13:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  有事相求
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我知道了  美希那边拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  没想到千早连社长那边也去过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  一直都很想来这的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是完全没想到该和谁商量什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.72,0:14:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  说不定有点忽略了身边的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.25,0:14:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  像这样大家聚在一起真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香要是在的话  一定会很开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  早就该来商量了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.51,0:14:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话  春香她也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  今天千早把我们叫来的原因是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有话想要说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于春香的事  还有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.97,0:14:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于我们的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春春和…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  怎么这样  我不会唱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.43,0:15:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  能唱的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  就算难听也会听的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  又这么欺负人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉就像是真和伊织一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那个人是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.45,0:15:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很像哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐  姐姐是天海春香吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真人啦  和电视里的一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.71,0:15:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  唱歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌啦  唱歌啦  唱歌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就稍微一会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  声音太小了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不要这么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以啦  要大家一起开心地…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.34,0:16:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  大家唱得很棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喜欢唱歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.28,0:16:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香长大了要做偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为偶像  然后和大家一起开心地唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家一起  开心地…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.45,0:16:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.42,0:16:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家共度时光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家一起前进
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久前还是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却因为我们个人的工作越来越多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得很难实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.95,0:17:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  个人的进步对偶像来说也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活动范围变大的话也难免会有所错过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想  春香因此才什么都没有说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  一直都主动叫我们的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说「来一起为了演唱会练习吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.15,0:17:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅是单纯的想练习
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是「想在一起」的心理表现
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「必须要改变」和「不想改变」的两种想法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.41,0:17:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都纠缠在心中  让春香苦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.58,0:18:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香请假就是这个原因吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不说出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算说出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.24,0:18:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算说出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.79,0:18:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没什么不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  应该是由我们发现才对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.06,0:18:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.56,0:18:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是千早不告诉我的话  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不只是为了春香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我无法歌唱的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.43,0:18:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是春香和大家伸出援手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.57,0:18:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对现在的我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,765事务所是我新的家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把工作放在第一位或许是我们的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不想放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.01,0:18:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  请帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  居然在这么重要的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  会议拖了不少时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会议？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.49,0:19:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  虽然还没和大家说过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「直播吗」的后续节目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想让美希单独来做那个节目的主持
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.37,0:19:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是我回绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.82,0:19:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为好像会找不到该走的路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.32,0:19:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希啊  很喜欢做偶像的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为能够闪闪发光  兴奋不已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只看着前面  跑得越来越远
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.99,0:19:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.19,0:19:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样继续前进的话  搞不好会迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:20:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够走出去  是因为有个能说「我回来了」的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里有会对我笑的人在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里的人  会对着我微笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家一起开心地…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌  跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.36,0:20:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小就是这样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是觉得大家「会不会不愿意呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.46,0:20:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到我的「和大家一起开心地…」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.04,0:20:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会成为大家的负担呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就变得害怕起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:20:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信大家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.05,0:21:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.94,0:21:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.61,0:21:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,765事务  新年演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.43,0:21:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎各位光临
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.67,0:21:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  要来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了能给各位最棒的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家会一起全力加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.22,0:21:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  咦  好像少了一个人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.15,0:21:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.01,0:22:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  让你等那么久  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.60,0:22:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在老地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.65,0:22:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在一起等你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.69,0:22:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见面  然后好好聊天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.82,0:22:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.21,0:22:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在属于我们的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.27,0:22:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.02,0:22:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.75,0:23:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.85,0:23:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.50,0:23:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周的偶像大师
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.76,0:24:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  我们765事务
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.23,0:24:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远都和大家在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.24,0:24:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  我们闪耀的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.10,0:24:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请一起来享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.02,0:24:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Comment: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:51.91,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}輝いたステージに立てば
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:57.57,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}最高の気分を味わえる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.57,0:16:01.19,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}すべてが報われる瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:04.04,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつまでも続け
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:08.90,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夢なら覚めないでいて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:14.46,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大空を飛ぶ鳥のように
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:20.13,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}翼を広げて羽ばたきたい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:23.60,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どんなに遠くても行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:26.40,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}憧れの世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:28.60,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夢だけでは…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:51.91,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只要站上耀眼的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:57.57,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就能尝到最棒的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.57,0:16:01.19,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}付出的一切得到回报的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:04.04,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}永远地继续着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:08.90,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如果是梦的话请不要醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:14.46,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}想像天空中的飞鸟一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:20.13,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}展翅飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:23.60,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无论路有多远  也不能阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:26.40,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}走向憧憬的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:28.60,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只有梦想…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.36,0:22:16.65,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}恋したり  夢描(えが)いたりすると
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.03,0:22:26.16,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}胸の奥に  複雑な気持ちが生まれるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.59,0:22:31.67,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今  大人になる道の途中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.91,0:22:41.74,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あふれる初体験  毎日を飾る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.70,0:22:52.11,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}だけど  この空がいつも私のこと見守ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.54,0:22:58.20,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}もっともっと強く  励ましてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.46,0:23:08.28,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}だから  怖くない  どこでも行きたいところに行ける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.06,0:23:16.01,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}輝いた未来  まっすぐにね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.01,0:23:22.08,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}きっとうまく超えられると
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.08,0:23:30.56,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Happyな思考回路でLet's  Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:43.03,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}決めた!  今すぐに  笑顔しかない私になって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.39,0:23:51.70,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}最高の未来  突き進む
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.36,0:22:16.65,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}恋爱啊  描绘梦想的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.03,0:22:26.16,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}内心里  就会产生复杂的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.59,0:22:31.67,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}现在  成长的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.91,0:22:41.74,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好多好多的第一次  装饰着每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.70,0:22:52.11,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不过  这片天空一直在守望着我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.54,0:22:58.20,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}要变得更加坚强  如此鼓励着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.46,0:23:08.28,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以不害怕  无论是哪里想去就能到达
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.06,0:23:16.01,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}向着闪耀的未来  笔直地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.01,0:23:22.08,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一定能顺利度过的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.08,0:23:30.56,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}以这样快乐的思考回路  Let's  Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:43.03,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}决定了！  现在就开始  成为只有笑容的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.39,0:23:51.70,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}向着最棒的未来  冲刺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:20:00.63,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたがいる　そんな風景が
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:08.16,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あたりまえだと思っていたの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:15.42,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}だけど少し変わり始めた日々
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.81,0:20:27.61,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}最初はいそがしいことも嬉しいよねって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:33.22,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}気持ち隠してメールすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:40.81,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}せつない心は凍えていくの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.41,0:20:54.54,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「いつもありがとう、がんばって」胸が詰まって言えない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:21:04.37,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつでも応援してるよと伝えたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:13.92,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}私も頑張ろう　頼ってばかりダメだね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.26,0:21:22.39,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}また会うその日は笑顔を見て欲しいから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:29.00,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泣いちゃおう　今は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:20:00.63,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}有你在的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:08.16,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}曾觉得是理所当然的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:15.42,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不知何时起  这样的日子逐渐减少
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.81,0:20:27.61,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}嘴上说着「忙碌是好事」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:33.22,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}发着违心的短信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:40.81,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那悲伤的心就渐渐结冰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.41,0:20:54.54,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「谢谢  加油」憋在心里说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:21:04.37,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我想告诉你我永远支持你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:13.92,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我也会加油  不能总是依靠你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.26,0:21:22.39,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}重逢的日子我想用笑容迎接你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:29.00,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}现在就放开哭吧


